- PASS requires evidence for every acceptance criterion. Missing worker evidence, source/build drift, or an unrelated green test suite is `INCONCLUSIVE` or `FAIL`, not PASS.
- PASS on rendered/live UI state cannot be based on source grep or bundle grep. For visual layers, CSS data-URL SVGs, and i18n, post browser DOM/snapshot output plus computed style/background-image, screenshot/pixel, Playwright locator, or DOM text evidence from the live page.
