{% elif identity_dev_acp_flow == "review_only" %}
- Review gate applies: post one verdict comment per review/recheck, then use `structured-review-verdict`; do not tag `@lead` in normal verdict comments because the review-events API wakes the lead after storing the structured event. Do not move implementation status or leave worker handoff comments.
